				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">For the Wikipedia mediation process for resolving disputes, see <a href="Wikipedia_Mediation" title="Wikipedia:Mediation">Wikipedia:Mediation</a>.  For contemplative exercises, see <a href="Meditation" title="Meditation">Meditation</a>.</div>
